01:55:52.000 --> 01:55:55.000
And by doing that, it's like self-talk.

01:55:55.000 --> 01:56:02.000
You're speaking to your subconscious, and your subconscious is going to refer back to that as a false memory.

01:56:02.000 --> 01:56:11.000
Because it's a positive reinforcement, it teaches you because of pattern recognition and over and over again being exposed to the same elements.

01:56:11.000 --> 01:56:15.000
And you're reinforcing yourself with your own comments and your own cheerleading.

01:56:16.000 --> 01:56:24.000
You're fortifying your expectations going forward on this pattern, yielding something in the past.

01:56:24.000 --> 01:56:34.000
Not that it's going to absolutely work in the future all the time, but we as price action traders, we look for signatures that repeat.

01:56:34.000 --> 01:56:36.000
Nothing is guaranteed that's going to repeat.

01:56:36.000 --> 01:56:38.000
